    "dcterms:abstract": [
        {
            "@language": "ja",
            "@value": "洗練された演出と俳優の豊かな身体性で日本の名作戯曲を現代化し、注目を集めているエイチエムピー・シアターカンパニーの新作は、歌舞伎や文楽の金字塔「忠臣蔵」を上演します。 元禄年間の大事件「赤穂事件」を題材にした「忠臣蔵」を、現代の視点から大胆に解釈し、今回は、赤穂城の明け渡しから吉良邸討ち入り、吉良の首級をあげるまでを描きます。 「主君に対する忠義心」が美談として語られ、今も人気が絶えない「忠臣蔵」の世界をシュルレアリスム的感性で切り込みます。\r\nあらすじ\r\nいつまで謎のままなのか。浅野内匠頭を追いつめ、殿中（江戸城）で刀を抜き、吉良上野介に斬り付けたものの正体。三百年も前だからわからない。それですませて、できあいのモノガタリを芝居で何千何万回と繰り返した結果の今、なにがどうなっているのか。それも謎のまま― ここらでいっぺん、ランプ片手に謎のなかに入ってみよう。鬼は出る、蛇は出る、足元は崩れ、天に穴があき、ランプが刀にかわり、着ているものが火消し服になり、雪が舞い、首が落ちてくる。あゝ、そんな忠臣蔵。もう前へ進むしかない。",
            "is_public": true,
            "property_id": 19,
            "property_label": "Abstract",
            "type": "literal"
        },
        {
            "@language": "en",
            "@value": "The new work of the HMP Theater Company, which has modernized Japanese masterpiece dramas with a sophisticated production and the rich physicality of actors, will perform Kabuki and Bunraku’s monumental “Chushingura.” We boldly interpret “Chushingura,” which is based on the “Ako Incident” that occurred during the Genroku era, from a modern perspective. We instill a surrealist sensibility into “Chushingura,” which is still popular even today as a beautiful story about loyalty to a master.\r\n\r\nSynopsis\r\nHow long will this remain a mystery? The true identity of what confronted Lord Asano, forced him to draw his sword in the palace (Edo Castle), and attack Kira Uenosuke. We still do not know 300 years later. We’ve accepted that as is, and the result of repeating some ready-made story hundreds of thousands of times is…what exactly? It remains a mystery – let’s go exploring this riddle for a bit and shed some light on it. A demon comes out, a snake comes out, the feet collapse, a hole opens in the heavens, the lamp transforms into a sword, the clothes become those of a fire fighter, the snow falls, and heads will roll. Oh, that kind of Chushingura. We have no other way but forward.",
            "is_public": true,
            "property_id": 19,
            "property_label": "Abstract",
            "type": "literal"
        }
    ],
